data.description: Nestled in the serene woods of Florissant, Colorado, this enchanting 4-bedroom, 4-bathroom home sits on two private acres, offering a perfect blend of rustic charm and modern amenities. The property features a spacious formal living and dining area, ideal for hosting, while the large kitchen boasts maple cabinets, ample counter space, and a huge pantry. Adjacent to the kitchen, the cozy family room with a wood-burning stove provides a warm, inviting atmosphere. Upstairs, two master suites each offer full baths and walk-in closets, offering views of the surrounding forest. Additional living space is available above the garage, where a well-appointed auxiliary bedroom and bathroom serve as perfect guest quarters. Outdoor living is enhanced by a wrap-around covered porch and deck, ideal for entertaining or enjoying the tranquility of nature. Practical amenities include main-level laundry facilities with a sink, a large workshop with a workbench, and a circular driveway for convenience. The property also features a fenced backyard, a chicken coop, and space for goats, embracing the surrounding wildlife and forest landscape. This home is more than just a place to live—it’s a lifestyle, providing a perfect setting for relaxation, hobbies, and enjoying nature.
